text: Vodka O is a 75 proof whey vodka made in Australia by ASM Liquor. Expert vodka reviewers have given a number of accolades to Vodka O. Liquor ratings aggregator, Proof66.com, places Vodka O in the Top 10th percentile of the best vodkas in the world. ==See also== *List of vodkas ==References== ==External links== * Category:Australian vodkas Category:Companies established in 2003 Category:2003 establishments in Australia Category:Companies based in Sydney
